Universal Education Style
     Scientist have discovered that there many different styles of learning that students have such as
Visual Learner
Audio Learner
Hybrid Learner
Textual Learner
Active Learner
  All these students would benefit from having adept learning styles . for example if a teacher just uses one style of teaching the other students will not benefit but would rather be in a deficit of knowledge 